data.title: Silent Child
data.meta_description: Silent Child is a Georgia-based producer who debuted on Monstercat with his track Hate U/Miss U in collaboration with Lani Daye, which was released on March 8, 2022. March March 8, 2022: Silent Child released his debut Monstercat single, Hate U/Miss U in collaboration with Lani Daye. The song is...
